Install TeX Live:

Windows: Install MiKTeX (https://miktex.org/), and it will prompt users to install any packages it needs when it needs them. 
macOS: Install MacTeX (https://tug.org/mactex/), and it will install all packages in TeX Live.
Linux: $ sudo apt install texlive-latex-extra texlive-science texworks

Launch a TeX editor:

Windows/Linux: Launch TeXworks.
macOS: Launch TeXShop.

Edit and typeset TeX documents:

Open and edit a TeX document.
Typeset the document to view it as a PDF.